# {{ .ProjectName }}

A SQLite-first server-rendered Go web application.

## Quick Start

```sh
cp .env.example .env
make migrate-up
make start
```

Open `http://localhost:8080`.

## Runtime Commands

```sh
./app all
./app serve
./app worker
./app migrate status
```

## Development

```sh
make start
make start-web
make start-worker
make test
make check
make sqlc
```

Created with [go-spark](https://github.com/inkyvoxel/go-spark).

See `docs/generated-features.md` for the current feature matrix for this app.
